{"tid":1789733,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【正視聽】【有關本日有星火同盟手足被捕之跟進情況】","createTime":"2019-12-19T13:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T13:45:08.000Z","uid":258106,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b314214d6fce9538bb46b03da5a88b3355fdc984","tid":1789733,"uid":258106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"【有關本日有星火同盟手足被捕之跟進情況】<br />\n<br />\n有關是日﹝二零一九年十二月十九日﹞警方對星火同盟手足的拘捕行動，由於本案已進入法律程序，星火同盟暫不便向外發佈更多資訊。所有被捕手足個案已有律師跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方企圖以失實陳述，將本平台之運作扭曲成洗黑錢等惡意用途，意圖抹黑星火及其他支援頻道，本平台譴責此等抹黑行為。<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟在此感激各方的關心與支持。如有任何相關消息，我們將於本專頁公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HSBC 係幫凶啊</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5789a7a35b0d23a2e8e28e0844a87c355bcaa53a","tid":1789733,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手入去將星火推到上國際</span>"},{"pid":"0ec531098f7eeffb5ab326796e450a415d01449c","tid":1789733,"uid":258106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5789a7a35b0d23a2e8e28e0844a87c355bcaa53a","tid":1789733,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手入去將星火推到上國際</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"正經post 無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0ecc6c14362d5ea293d99f7dc80ecab111a28e","tid":17